snippet.title: C64 Game - Xenon Ranger
snippet.description:
Collect enough energy pods on the surface and deposit them at the teleport to allow you access to lower levels. Try to deactivate the switches removing the guardian robots protecting key passages. This will allow you access to the time gate. Beware! Your time underground is limited and you will return.

Released by Alpha Omega Software in 1988 and created by Finlay Munro. This deserved a bit more than 17% from the Zzap64 review. Well harsh. Hoots mon!
